  <brief_title>Impact of Omalizumab on Quality of Life Measures and Angioedema Occurrence in Patients With CSU Refractory to Therapy</brief_title>
  <acronym>X-ACT</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, 28-week Treatment With a 8 Week Follow-up to Investigate the Impact of Omalizumab on Quality of Life Measures and the Incidence and Severity of Angioedema Despite H1-antihistamine Therapy.</official_title>
